CHANGELOG
=========

0.3.0
-----
- Added route property 'Secure'
- Added route property 'REST'
- Added route property 'Host'
- Removed ability of closure-typed routes to modify its Execute. Althrough it
  can be very interesing feature to programmaticaly modify target that makes
  very hard to predict, track and debug routing. Best place to programmaticaly
  redirect routing is to intercept router event.

0.2.0
-----
- Refactored.
- Execution is striped out from component, it should be done by application.
- Path can contain optional segments.
- Route property 'Id' renamed to 'Name'.
- Route property 'Auth' removed, unauthorized visitor must see that URL is 
  correct but need to be authorized to see content.



